reviews: The oven mitt is fantastic but I wasn't reading properly and completely didn't notice the absence of the s in "Oven Mitt". I understand its my fault but I think it should be more clearly stated that there is only 1 oven mitt. I feel like a lot of people could miss that
nice quality beanie, fits the way I wanted it to and im very happy! I ordered the black beanie and it says it was made in Canada which was a big plus!
Took a while to get here but worth it :)
Got this bathing suit when it was on sale and omg it look amazing! I would recommend this swimsuit to anyone
